{"tid":808252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王者榮耀將接入公安數據庫 騰訊挫逾2%創一年低","createTime":"2018-09-06T07:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T07:54:10.000Z","uid":54373,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"16947be655dc86a55c1611c27e04fcca2962105a","tid":808252,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:47:14.000Z","msg":"內地《南方都市報》報道引述遊戲界人士指，內地未來會向每款遊戲徵收35%的專項稅，傳棋牌類遊戲會首先被徵稅。騰訊（700）今早開市急挫，至午市跌2.53%，報316.6元，創52周新低，暫成交27億元。<br />\n<br />\n內地早前已停止批新遊戲上線，上月教育部更限制青年人使用網絡遊戲時間，令遊戲業雪上加霜。<br />\n<br />\n中午騰訊官網宣布，旗下《王者榮耀》將啟動最嚴格的實名政策，會接入公安權威數據平台校驗，以判斷遊戲賬號實名訊息的玩家是否未成年，並據此決定賬號是否納入健康系統的防沉迷體系中。"},{"pid":"ee972adb74f3857fdce7663bda9d7fc768398717","tid":808252,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:48:31.000Z","msg":"大陸人既手段真係好低下<br />\n一味只係靠封<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f905e688fe9717b8f68f1ba0ac3deec16a6fbf5c","tid":808252,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ee972adb74f3857fdce7663bda9d7fc768398717","tid":808252,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:48:31.000Z","msg":"大陸人既手段真係好低下<br />\n一味只係靠封<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:49:00.000Z","msg":"可能公安有裝備賣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0341c92948bb346bcc5e130689268f4ba057d8db","tid":808252,"uid":191926,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:51:53.000Z","msg":"公安部守護兒童基金<br />\n<br />\n課金1000蚊 一個月 每日打4小時<br />\n課多5000蚊 一個月 每月玩8小時<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e8508639cd0a4d02eaa3088522e89c718314df","tid":808252,"uid":58413,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0341c92948bb346bcc5e130689268f4ba057d8db","tid":808252,"uid":191926,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:51:53.000Z","msg":"公安部守護兒